  			<p>Our popular <a href="http://bizoptix.com">BizOptix</a> technology platform provides users with an immediate server connection, application access, and an online viewing/reporting environment that can be used to create, view and modify business content.</p>
            <p>Built on BizOptix, and leveraging our security and compliance roots, the <a href="riskoptix.html">RiskOptix</a> application is a stand-alone Enterprise Risk Management solution that is popular with financial institutions nationwide.</p>
            <p>Finally, for a select group of customers, our Information Security Consulting Services are available to provide direct access to our security engineers.</p>
